tracks.feedDescription: The drunk at the bar next to you is determined to ruin your silent reflection. Their blabbering slowly evolves from jibberish to coherent, and from coherent to brilliant.  They have tapped into exactly what you needed to hear somehow.  An annoyance turned into therapy all because you were too lazy to get up.
